summary: This document is a summons report issued by the New York City Police Department related to a violation involving Ghislaine Maxwell. The report details the vehicle information and the circumstances surrounding the summons, including the date and location of the violation.

persons.name: Ghislaine Maxwell

events.title: Parking Violation Summons
events.description: A parking violation summons was issued for Ghislaine Maxwell's vehicle for double parking.

keyFacts: Ghislaine Maxwell was issued a parking violation summons on September 3, 2011.
The vehicle involved was a black 2007 Cadillac with Florida plates.
The summons was issued for a violation of double parking.
